q: SELECT e/ehr_id/value, c/uid/value, o/name/value, l/value/value FROM EHR e CONTAINS COMPOSITION c CONTAINS OBSERVATION o[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.symptom_sign_screening.v0, 'Husten'] CONTAINS ELEMENT l[name/value='Vorhanden?'] WHERE (c/archetype_details/template_id/value MATCHES {'Corona_Anamnese', 'Corona_Anamnese2'} AND e/ehr_id/value MATCHES {'f13a5e18-a2db-473e-af61-784246ddd8a6', 'dc03d1c7-098e-4a7a-8503-4a6f305ddeea'})
